      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (5.8M cells), fine (14.2M cells). GCI on NIH: 3.7% (medium-to-fine). Richardson-extrapolated NIH used as reference. Asymptotic convergence confirmed (GCI ratio 1.02). Discretization error meets Gradation 2 requirement."
