      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) defined as ratio of predicted NIH to experimental NIH. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 (non-inferiority). All 5 operating points satisfy RH < 1. Mean absolute percentage error 8.3%. Formal validation metric defined prior to simulation execution. Gradation 2 satisfied."
