      "rationale": "NIH and RH are the standard hemolysis quantification metrics per ASTM F1841 and FDA guidance. These QoIs directly map to the clinical endpoint of erythrocyte damage. Relevance of QoIs to COU decision is high. Gradation 2 requirement met."
    },
    {
