      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used for both validation and COU analysis. Operating conditions (3–7 L/min, 2500–4000 RPM) span CPB clinical range. Bovine blood surrogate used in experiments with matched viscosity. Validation-to-COU relevance assessed as high. Gradation 2 achieved."
