      "rationale": "Not assessed as standalone factor at MRL 2. SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for centrifugal pump hemolysis studies. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model applied consistently with prior FDA pump studies. Model form justification documented in simulation plan; formal assessment deferred at MRL 2."
    },
    {
