    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 provisions for MRL 2 Class II devices. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within 8.3% of experimental benchmark across all 5 operating points with RH < 1 at all conditions. Discretization error controlled (GCI 3.7%). Model is considered credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in support of the CPB device submission decision.",
